headlines.description: Leeds United's returning striker Patrick Bamford struck in added time as they snatched a 2-2 Premier League draw against Brentford on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bamford snatches late point for Leeds

headlines.description: Manchester United earned a 1-0 win over Crystal Palace on new manager Ralf Rangnick's debut thanks to Fred's second-half goal.
headlines.shortLinkText: Man Utd win on Rangnick bow thanks to Fred goal

headlines.description: — Antonio Conte’s unbeaten run in the Premier League at Tottenham goes on.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tottenham beats Norwich 3-0, Kane's goal drought continues

headlines.description: — Ezri Konsa scored twice as Aston Villa rallied to beat Leicester 2-1 in the Premier League on Sunday and continue its revival under Steven Gerrard.
headlines.shortLinkText: Konsa double earns Villa 2-1 win over Leicester in EPL
